&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Founded in 2017,&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.trip-arc.com/&quot;&gt;TripArc&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;is a $750 million privately held company powers the top Travel Agencies and Tour Operators in North America. Our expansive and growing network empowers seamless access to a comprehensive range of travel options and services globally with over $750 million transactions annually - all at the industry’s best rates.&lt;/p&gt;
